## ⚙️ Features

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Font** | OpenDyslexic (local OTF file) |
| **Line Height** | 1.4 – 2.0 (slider) |
| **Letter Spacing** | 0 – 0.20em (slider) |
| **Word Spacing** | 0 – 0.40em (slider) |
| **Font Size** | 80% – 150% (slider) |
| **Themes** | Light / Sepia / Dark |
| **Dark Mode** | Body only, images untouched |
| **Paragraph Highlight** | Hover highlight for focus reading |
| **Persistence** | chrome.storage.local (survives restart) |
| **Non-destructive** | Only targets text elements, never `*` |

---

## 🔒 Privacy

- No network requests
- No data collection
- No analytics
- All settings stored locally via `chrome.storage.local`

---

## 📄 Permissions Explained

| Permission | Why |
|------------|-----|
| `storage` | Save your settings across sessions |
| `activeTab` | Send messages to the current tab |
| `scripting` | Inject content script dynamically |
| `<all_urls>` | Apply reading aids on any website |
